ASoC: Intel: boards: add support for adl boards in sof-rt5682

ADL customer boards are with below 2 configurations

Board 1: RT5682 on SSP0 and MAX98373 on SSP1
Board 2: RT5682 on SSP0 and MAX98357A on SSP2

